{"tid":1610371,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"偽勇唔好再增加前線壓力","createTime":"2019-10-01T17:14:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T17:59:47.000Z","uid":236658,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3cbc938921dacbf9d4957c799655c7c9b6a0b6af","tid":1610371,"uid":236658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:14:36.000Z","msg":"Full晒gear為既係可以行前多少少食花生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真心覺得未ready既 做和理非都無問題 但真係唔好亂咁製造恐慌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地full gear 其實可以行前親眼睇清楚咩環境 再唔係問清楚手足咩情況都得 了解清楚啲先 唔好有人話跑就真係跑走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地齊裝咁跑 搞到班和理非以為真勇都走 可以徹 最後掉低班真勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />叫你地上翻前真係辛苦過食彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當真勇武決定左推 班偽勇遲遲唔郁 人地和理非就真係唔行架啦<br />\n氹掂你地 前線人數多翻啲 人地都佈晒防增晒援啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n齊晒裝既 唔該諗清楚自己既定位 買完套gear 究竟可以點樣幫到前面<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"4646ee40d29f9ccf5f801e7ddb4161163aef3e5e","tid":1610371,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:18:06.000Z","msg":"請全民無&middot;限&middot;期罷工罷課，救自己、救義士！迫政府讓步！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1610341\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1610341</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a0511a689fe21abd2b41f26d690e483d571e9ccb","tid":1610371,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:18:19.000Z","msg":"和理非見到偽勇 唔知係想轉位呀定趕去邊 走得勁撚快<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n搞撚到大恐慌"},{"pid":"4633b276cb9f842f732f1eb88e5c87b6d8d89d54","tid":1610371,"uid":13586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:19:02.000Z","msg":"我係喺灣仔嬲到喊嘅勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由海富老江湖勇武話上橋打狗<br />\n然後咩子彈都出<br />\n之後個個full gear偽勇武跑步快過保特<br />\n<br />\n淨返好少手足先無奈撤退<br />\n仲要一路撤到和昌大押行，嬲到喊<br />\n<br />\n夠人有得打都變冇得打，好灰<br />\n<br />\n偽勇武聽住呀，話我分化撚都要屌！<br />\n我哋嘅敵人唔止黑警、林鄭、政府，仲有成個中共<br />\n中共點屠殺自己睇返中史教科書<br />\n三面紅旗，三反五反，文革批鬥，八九六四<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">簡稱「冇底線」呀！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n之前光明頂入面陶傑冇講錯<br />\n「而家係要用搞革命嘅方式嚟爭取好卑微嘅訴求」<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但有幾多人真係有搞革命嘅覺悟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n冇呢種覺悟<br />\n我寧願你縮返後半gear又好和理非都好<br />\n個個見到full gear跑嘅個個都驚<br />\n製造埋哂啲不必要嘅恐慌<br />\n<br />\n而家唔係跑online呀，打仗呀！戰場呀！屌你老母！<br />\n揾次真係推，打狗好唔好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19cd6c5062e58f73b4ae4991bf718d9b0959a453","tid":1610371,"uid":210691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:21:15.000Z","msg":"壓力就係 明明一開始好多人 一叫企疏小小 之後企企下唔我望一下後面 冇哂人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好彩呢日警力唔係主要搞我去個區 如果唔係比速龍捉哂"},{"pid":"fcd04fec1d1de7ef3cfd7e4e7f5c071370f980ed","tid":1610371,"uid":60393,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:21:32.000Z","msg":"起底 分化撚 block<br />\n<br />\n分你老母真同偽勇咩"},{"pid":"4fe9d38d17b7982b8d407d070382677a372f8c48","tid":1610371,"uid":186142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:23:32.000Z","msg":"阻阻你 入嚟討論下 幫手足報仇<br />\n呢個Post講明偽勇武可以點樣發揮作用<br />\n【戰術】唔想再比人拉入嚟推Post<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aiEjcjU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aiEjcjU</a>"},{"pid":"cd01f79581ea9f652fce4922c23678f537621ab5","tid":1610371,"uid":50347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19cd6c5062e58f73b4ae4991bf718d9b0959a453","tid":1610371,"uid":210691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"201